'''安傑莉卡·辛格頓·范布倫'''（{{lang-en|Angelica Singleton Van Buren}}，1818年2月13日－1877年12月29日）是{{link-en|亞伯拉罕·范布倫|Abraham Van Buren}}的妻子<ref name=":0">{{Cite book|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=KqeXCgAAQBAJ|title=America's First Ladies: A Historical Encyclopedia and Primary Document Collection of the Remarkable Women of the White House: A Historical Encyclopedia and Primary Document Collection of the Remarkable Women of the White House|last=Hendricks|first=Nancy|date=2015-10-13|publisher={{link-en|美國書目中心克利俄出版社|ABC-Clio}}|isbn=9781610698832|language=en|year=|location=|pages=|access-date=2021-01-27|archive-date=2020-07-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200726034755/https://books.google.com/books?id=KqeXCgAAQBAJ|dead-url=no}}</ref>、第八任[[美國總統|美國總統]][[馬丁·范布倫|馬丁·范布倫]]的[[兒媳|兒媳]]。安傑莉卡在她丈夫的母親[[漢娜·范布倫|漢娜·范布倫]]逝世且總統未有續娶的情況下，代理了[[美國第一夫人|美國第一夫人]]的職務，同時是美國史上最為年輕的[[白宮|白宮]]女主人<ref name="NFLL-Hannahvan">{{Cite web|title=First Lady Biography: Hannah Van Buren|url=http://www.firstladies.org/biographies/firstladies.aspx?biography=8|accessdate=2013-07-17|publisher=美國國家第一夫人圖書館|dead-url=no|location=俄亥俄州坎頓|archive-date=2018-10-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181009205029/http://www.firstladies.org/biographies/firstladies.aspx?biography=8}}</ref><ref name=":1">{{Cite book|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=AzPd0aVnOl0C|title=All the Presidents' Children: Triumph and Tragedy in the Lives of America's First Families|last=Wead|first=Doug|date=2004-01-06|publisher=[[西蒙與舒斯特|西蒙與舒斯特]]|isbn=9780743446334|language=en|year=|location=|pages=|access-date=2021-01-27|archive-date=2020-07-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200726041248/https://books.google.com/books?id=AzPd0aVnOl0C|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=":3">{{Cite book|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=77u4CwAAQBAJ&pg=PA139e|title=A Companion to First Ladies|last=Sibley|first=Katherine A. S.|date=2016-03-02|publisher=[[約翰威立|約翰威立]]|isbn=9781118732243|language=en|year=|location=|pages=|access-date=2021-01-27|archive-date=2020-07-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200726034214/https://books.google.com/books?id=77u4CwAAQBAJ&pg=PA139e|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

